Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.45,0:23:05.53,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:11.20,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:16.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:22.29,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,I... to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.08,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,...might love you...
