Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:52.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}Her Highness's {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:41.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:41.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Vow of Wind and Water
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...return to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real sailor uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out, Louise. This is Japan's Akiba{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:00:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:00:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I came back to Japan by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was summoned as a familiar to a strange world by an incompetent mage, Louise,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was dragged into a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found this Zero and finally managed to come back, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in coming back to Japan without Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, I thought you went away somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making a ruckus out of your dream, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been a little full of yourself lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did give up on returning to your world and chose to stay as my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I won't call you a dog anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make you sleep on the floor or whip you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better take your eyes off the maid\Nand the other girls and look only at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a familiar, so it's only natural for you to look only at your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, then go back to sleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you guys say to each other, you're getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder how long that'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall now explain the procedure for leaving the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Masarini...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need a crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here you are being selfish again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are in the middle of a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although we have halted Albion's\Nmarch, we cannot let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens are wishing for you to become the true Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and defeat the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise Princess Henrietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Praise Tristain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the coronation ceremony, so I bet even a captive like myself would be served a special meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there's no Last Supper for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cromwell,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how foolish of you to become a captive after going through...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the trouble of killing the prince of Albion to gain authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, in the midst of the coronation ceremony, I was able to retrieve the Ring of Andvari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, give me another chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used a magic I've never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge light appeared all of a sudden and annihilated my troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Void?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, that was completely unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not my responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You'll never have to take responsibility again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess' parade is going to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, I have a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a pair of glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have fine eyesight if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't an ordinary pair of glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked my elder sister to send one of our family treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you have an elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put them on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I remember you saying that you're the youngest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you working today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go check out the parade with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you have given up returning to your home for Miss Vallière's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... What's with those glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Medusa's Glasses are a magical item.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any time you look at a girl other than myself, the one who gave them to you, with lascivious eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the gems around them glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need only look at your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stare at other girls when you're a familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With lustrous eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With dilated eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With bloodshot eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly were you looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That maid's face, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...her breasts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You were looking at her boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.65,0:09:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you like big ones that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you like big boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the bigger ones are better for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's Miss Vallière and Saito-kun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Montmorency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two off to watch the parade as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two get along well as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like us, Montmorency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since today's a day to celebrate, I'm wearing an outgoing dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:23.05,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a little short?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's those two again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand Kirche, but who\Nknew you were eyeing Tabitha, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is "female" the only trait that you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't look at anyone else anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep your eyes shut until we go back to our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing closing your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so majestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you eye the Princess... no, the Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Louise! Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.10,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a ruffian!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect Our Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain. I assume it was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Her Highness' court lady, Louise de La Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk with Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been ordered to not let anybody through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,La Vallière-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop your wand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun is faster than spell casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness is in a meeting with Principal Osmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall hear what you need to say in her stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Principal Osmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes Chevalier de Milan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Musketeer Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Musketeer Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that arrested Saito, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito isn't the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caused the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The idiot was eyeing the Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, give me back Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with this present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm treated like this, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise will get married with some stupid aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll praise the two from afar,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and end my life as a familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I should have returned to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't return home, then I'd rather pick a different girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favour to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you desire so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You insolent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you touch the hands of the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shoot you right this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes, please stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I will shoot you regardless of what Her Highness says!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the information gathered by Intelligence and from what Principal Osmond said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was you and Louise who defeated the Albion force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are certain that it was done by the void mage and her familiar, Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you lend us your power?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the entire country is at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The military in particular is saying we should take the opportunity and march into Albion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cardinal Masarini and the senior statesmen seem to agree with the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to avoid war, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the Gandalfr's insignia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, along with Louise, help me with your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Louise said that she'd do anything if it's for you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:17:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am asking you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please become one of my few allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the few?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a Queen is inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only a handful of people who can truly understand and help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, please stay at the Magic Academy with Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep you two undercover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies exist within the Kingdom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spies, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few hours ago, inside the jail for aristocrats,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Cromwell was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A multi-layered Lock spell had been cast there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who could dispel a Lock must have led the culprit through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that really happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anything you want as a reward for your cooperation, please say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it is within my capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please bring Miss Vallière over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You got it wrong! You got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you make me worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heresiarch's Book of Invocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess gave it to me.{the?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that it'd be better for me to hold onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, it's passed down through the Tristain's royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Principal Osmond's research,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,void spells should be written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should be? But there's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A misprint?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you figure something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White paper. In other words, nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fight with an empty mind", perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sparkle~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you often see that kind of line in manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I haven't read manga in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, do you feel that you should have returned home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave you alone in a dangerous place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, Miss Vallière, the Queen's words shall be\Npassed down to you via a member of the Musketeer Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The code name for you two is Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hiraga Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall overlook today, but if you act in a perverse manner towards the Queen in the future, be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this "perverse manner"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog in heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hentai Dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar, you said that you'd never call me a dog or whip me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:57.61,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare talk back to me, perverted dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you wag your tail at every girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to... the... the... P-Pri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priceless Joumon artefact?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting lecherously towards the Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Louise! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that this was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vallière-dono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it is an emergency, so forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.11,0:21:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen has been kidnapped by somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog, get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess got taken away by Prince Wales, who's supposed to have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vow of Wind and Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
